stateDiagram-v2
    [*] --> Created: store_memory
    Created --> Retrieved: recall_memory
    Retrieved --> Updated: update_memory
    Updated --> Retrieved: recall_memory
    Retrieved --> Associated: associate_memories
    Associated --> Retrieved: recall_memory
    Updated --> Associated: associate_memories
    Retrieved --> Deleted: delete_memory
    Updated --> Deleted: delete_memory
    Associated --> Deleted: delete_memory
    Deleted --> [*]
    
    note right of Created
        Initial state after storage
        Has memory_id, content, tags
    end note
    
    note right of Updated
        Modified fields preserved
        memory_id unchanged
        updated_at timestamp set
    end note
    
    note right of Deleted
        Permanent removal
        Embedding deleted from Qdrant
        Node removed from FalkorDB
    end note